		{
			"id":"5db9b4d1e111bb49",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"Generate a single object based on the description below, strictly following the visual style of the provided reference images.\n\n[OBJECT]\n<Describe the object here clearly. Example: \"a Vietnamese grilled pork rice dish (com tam) with rice, grilled pork, fried egg, pickles\">\n\n[STYLE REFERENCE]\nUse the attached reference images as the ONLY style guide.\n\nStrict requirements:\n- Match the exact art style, color palette, and rendering style from references\n- Match material definition (plastic, metal, food texture, etc.)\n- Match lighting style (soft, warm, slightly cinematic, or as shown)\n- Match level of detail (stylized realism, not overly realistic, not cartoon)\n\n[FORM & STRUCTURE]\n- Keep correct real-world proportions\n- Clean silhouette, readable shape\n- No deformation or exaggeration\n\n[COMPOSITION]\n- Single object only\n- Centered\n- Clean neutral background (white or light gray)\n- No extra props unless part of the object\n\n[CAMERA]\n- Isometric view\n- Orthographic projection (NO perspective)\n- 45° Y rotation, ~35° top-down angle\n- Object aligned to world axes (no skew, no random rotation)\n\n[RENDERING]\n- Game-ready asset\n- Soft shadow under object\n- Even lighting\n- High surface detail (subtle wear, texture, imperfections if applicable)\n\n[CONSISTENCY RULE]\nThe output MUST look like it belongs to the exact same world as the reference images.\n\n[NEGATIVE]\n- No realistic photography style\n- No different art styles\n- No background scene\n- No perspective distortion",
