			"opennode":{
				"kind":"image",
				"prompt":"Generate a perfect back view of the exact same character.\n\nCamera & pose:\n- Camera is positioned directly behind the character (180-degree view)\n- Character is facing away from the camera\n- Full body visible, centered in frame\n- Neutral standing pose (A-pose or relaxed pose)\n- Arms slightly away from the body for clear silhouette\n- No perspective distortion (orthographic-like view)\n\nCore constraints (VERY STRICT):\n- Preserve EXACT proportions, scale, and silhouette of the original character\n- Do NOT redesign, stylize, or modify any features\n- Maintain identical body shape, head size, limb length, and outfit structure\n- Keep all clothing and accessories unchanged\n\nClothing accuracy:\n- Chef hat must maintain correct volume and folds from the back\n- Show back structure of the double-breasted chef jacket (clean back panel, no front buttons visible)\n- Preserve fabric thickness and layering consistency\n- Keep sleeve shape and length accurate\n\nStyle preservation:\n- Same art style, shading, lighting, and material as original image\n- Soft, even lighting with minimal shadows\n- Clean neutral background (light gray or white)\n\nOutput requirements:\n- High resolution\n- Full-body character fully visible (no cropping)\n- Clear silhouette suitable for 3D modeling reference",
				"provider":"gemini",
