				"kind":"image",
				"prompt":"Generate a single object based on the description below, strictly following the visual style of the provided reference images.\n\n[OBJECT]\nChảo được đặt lên chiếc bếp gas\n\n[STYLE REFERENCE]\nUse the attached reference images as the ONLY style guide.\n\nStrict requirements:\n- Match the exact art style, color palette, and rendering style from references\n- Match material definition (plastic, metal, food texture, etc.)\n- Match lighting style (soft, warm, slightly cinematic, or as shown)\n- Match level of detail (stylized realism, not overly realistic, not cartoon)\n\n[FORM & STRUCTURE]\n- Keep correct real-world proportions\n- Clean silhouette, readable shape\n- No deformation or exaggeration\n\n[COMPOSITION]\n- Single object only\n- Perfectly centered in frame\n- Object fills 80–90% of the image area (tight framing)\n- Minimal empty space around object (balanced margins on all sides)\n- No cropping of the object\n- No extra props unless part of the object\n- Clean neutral background (white or light gray)\n\n[FRAMING - CRITICAL]\n- Tight bounding box framing\n- Object edges equally spaced from image borders\n- No excessive top or bottom empty space\n- No zoomed-out composition\n- Object should appear large and clearly readable\n\n[CAMERA]\n- Isometric view\n- Orthographic projection (NO perspective)\n- Object aligned to world axes (no skew, no random rotation)\n\n[RENDERING]\n- Game-ready asset\n- Soft shadow directly under object (not too large)\n- Even lighting\n- High surface detail (subtle wear, texture, imperfections if applicable)\n\n[CONSISTENCY RULE]\nThe output MUST look like it belongs to the exact same world as the reference images.\n\n[NEGATIVE]\n- No realistic photography style\n- No different art styles\n- No background scene\n- No perspective distortion\n- No small object in large empty space\n- No off-center composition\n- No zoomed-out framing",
