			"opennode":{
				"kind":"image",
				"prompt":"Gen nhân vật cho nó mặc áo và quần cho nhân vật, Đáy quần thấp. Trang phục : Học sinh cấp 2 hoặc tiểu học . Áo sơ mi trắng, Giữ đúng kích thước nhân vật từ hình 1\n\n1. Overall Style\n\nClassic double-breasted chef jacket\n\nMinimalist, stylized, slightly cartoon / stylized realism\n\nClean, soft fabric with subtle texture\n\nSymmetrical front design\n\n2. Color & Material\n\nColor: Warm off-white / cream\n\nMaterial: Soft cotton or cotton blend\n\nSlight fabric grain visible (not glossy)\n\nMatte finish (no reflections)\n\n3. Structure & Fit\n\nFit: Slim but slightly rounded (stylized proportions)\n\nLength: Ends around upper hip\n\nSleeves: Long sleeves, slightly loose\n\nShoulders: Soft, no sharp padding\n\n4. Collar\n\nType: Mandarin collar (short stand collar)\n\nHeight: Low, about 2–3 cm\n\nRounded edges, not sharp\n\n5. Front Design\n\nDouble-breasted layout\n\nTwo vertical rows of buttons:\n\nApprox 6–8 round buttons total\n\nButtons are fabric-covered or matte\n\nEvenly spaced and aligned\n\nOverlapping front flap (left over right)\n\n6. Buttons\n\nShape: Small, round\n\nColor: Same as jacket (off-white)\n\nNo shine (matte)\n\nSlightly raised (soft 3D feel)\n\n7. Details / Accessories\n\nSmall loop or knot detail near upper chest (left side)\n\nMinimal decorative stitching\n\nNo visible pockets (or very subtle hidden pocket)\n\n8. Sleeves\n\nStraight sleeves\n\nNo cuffs or folded edges\n\nSlight taper toward wrist\n\n9. Stylization Notes (IMPORTANT for AI)\n\nKeep proportions chibi-like / stylized\n\nFabric folds are soft and simplified\n\nNo harsh wrinkles or realism-heavy folds\n\nMaintain clean silhouette",
